      <title>农民工资上涨提振供应前景，可可价格暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/cocoa-slumps-as-farmer-pay-hikes-boost-supply-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[可可价格连续第三天下跌，原因是看涨势头失去动力，农民工资上涨的前景增加了西非供应增加的希望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/cocoa-slumps-as-farmer-pay-hikes-boost-supply-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 10:44:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
