      <title>印度小盘股在 800 亿美元暴跌后数周内卷土重来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/india-smallcaps-recoup-losses-sparked-by-regulator-s-froth-alert</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度小盘股的一个关键指标收复了监管机构对市场泡沫的担忧引发的长达一个月的损失，因为股市崩盘为投资者提供了逢低买入的机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/india-smallcaps-recoup-losses-sparked-by-regulator-s-froth-alert</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 04:02:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
